        <ontology:description xml:lang="no">Ontologi som beskriver marine observatorier (regionale fasiliteter, steder, plattformer) for å støtte FAIR datastyring og interoperabilitet, spesielt i EMSO ERIC-konteksten.</ontology:description>
        <ontology:description xml:lang="ro">Ontologia care descrie observatoarele marine (facilități regionale, situri, platforme) pentru a susține gestionarea FAIR a datelor și interoperabilitatea, în special în contextul EMSO ERIC.</ontology:description>
        <ontology:description xml:lang="it">Ontologia che descrive gli osservatori marini (infrastrutture regionali, siti, piattaforme) per supportare la gestione FAIR dei dati e l’interoperabilità, in particolare nel contesto EMSO ERIC.</ontology:description>
        <ontology:description xml:lang="pt">Ontologia que descreve os observatórios marinhos (infraestruturas regionais, locais, plataformas) para apoiar a gestão FAIR de dados e a interoperabilidade, especialmente no contexto do EMSO ERIC.</ontology:description>
        <ontology:description xml:lang="fr">Ontologie décrivant les observatoires marins (infrastructures régionales, sites, plateformes) pour soutenir la gestion FAIR des données et l’interopérabilité, notamment dans le cadre d’EMSO ERIC.</ontology:description>
        <ontology:description xml:lang="en">Ontology describing marine observatories (Regional Facilities, Sites, Platforms) to support FAIR data management and interoperability, particularly in the EMSO ERIC context.</ontology:description>
        <ontology:description xml:lang="es">Ontología que describe los observatorios marinos (infraestructuras regionales, sitios, plataformas) para apoyar la gestión FAIR de datos y la interoperabilidad, especialmente en el contexto de EMSO ERIC.</ontology:description>
        <ontology:description xml:lang="el">Οντολογία που περιγράφει τα θαλάσσια παρατηρητήρια (περιφερειακές υποδομές, τοποθεσίες, πλατφόρμες) για την υποστήριξη της διαχείρισης δεδομένων FAIR και της διαλειτουργικότητας, ιδιαίτερα στο πλαίσιο του EMSO ERIC.</ontology:description>
