        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="ro">A nu se confunda cu OpenScienceOntology (OSO) sau cu Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO).</skos:scopeNote>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="it">Da non confondere con OpenScienceOntology (OSO) o Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO).</skos:scopeNote>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="no">Må ikke forveksles med OpenScienceOntology (OSO) eller Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO).</skos:scopeNote>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="es">No confundir con OpenScienceOntology (OSO) ni con Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO).</skos:scopeNote>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">Not to be confused with OpenScienceOntology (OSO) or Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO).</skos:scopeNote>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="pt">Não confundir com OpenScienceOntology (OSO) nem com Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO).</skos:scopeNote>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="fr">À ne pas confondre avec OpenScienceOntology (OSO) ni avec Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO).</skos:scopeNote>
        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="el">Να μην συγχέεται με το OpenScienceOntology (OSO) ή το Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO).</skos:scopeNote>
