    <!-- https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Marha -->


    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Marha">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#FundedProject"/>
        <foaf:homepage rdf:resource="https://www.life-marha.fr/"/>
        <OSO:Project_is_led_by_an_Organization rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#Office_français_de_la_biodiversité"/>
        <OSO:hasCountry rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO#France"/>
        <OSO:hasLogo rdf:resource="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/emso-eric/oso-ontology/574ea01da2510994a290bef4699695d5e0fd86dc/images/life_marha.jpg"/>
        <terms:description xml:lang="no">Det integrerte LIFE-prosjektet Marha (Marine Habitats) har som mål å gjenopprette og opprettholde en god bevaringstilstand for naturlige marine habitater i fastlands-Frankrike. Fra 2018 til 2025 ble mer enn 650 tiltak innen vurdering, utprøving, forvaltning, bevisstgjøring og opplæring gjennomført, med deltakelse fra alle aktører involvert i forvaltningen av marine Natura 2000-områder.</terms:description>
        <terms:description xml:lang="es">El proyecto integrado LIFE Marha (Marine Habitats) tiene como objetivo restaurar y mantener el buen estado de conservación de los hábitats marinos naturales en la Francia metropolitana. Entre 2018 y 2025, se llevaron a cabo más de 650 acciones de evaluación, experimentación, gestión, sensibilización y formación, movilizando a todos los actores implicados en la gestión de los sitios Natura 2000 en el mar.</terms:description>
        <terms:description xml:lang="it">Il progetto LIFE integrato Marha (Marine Habitats) mira a ripristinare e mantenere il buono stato di conservazione degli habitat marini naturali nella Francia metropolitana. Dal 2018 al 2025 sono state realizzate oltre 650 azioni di valutazione, sperimentazione, gestione, sensibilizzazione e formazione, mobilitando tutti gli attori coinvolti nella gestione dei siti Natura 2000 marini.</terms:description>
        <terms:description xml:lang="fr">Le projet LIFE intégré Marha (Marine Habitats) vise à rétablir et à maintenir le bon état de conservation des habitats naturels marins en France hexagonale. De 2018 à 2025, plus de 650 actions d’évaluation, d’expérimentation, de gestion, de sensibilisation et de formation ont été mises en œuvre, en mobilisant l’ensemble des acteurs impliqués dans la gestion des sites Natura 2000 en mer.</terms:description>
        <terms:description xml:lang="pt">O projeto integrado LIFE Marha (Marine Habitats) tem como objetivo restaurar e manter o bom estado de conservação dos habitats marinhos naturais na França continental. Entre 2018 e 2025, foram implementadas mais de 650 ações de avaliação, experimentação, gestão, sensibilização e formação, mobilizando todos os atores envolvidos na gestão dos sítios Natura 2000 marinhos.</terms:description>
        <terms:description xml:lang="ro">Proiectul integrat LIFE Marha (Marine Habitats) are ca obiectiv restabilirea și menținerea unei stări favorabile de conservare a habitatelor marine naturale din Franța continentală. Între 2018 și 2025 au fost implementate peste 650 de acțiuni de evaluare, experimentare, gestionare, sensibilizare și formare, mobilizând toți actorii implicați în gestionarea siturilor marine Natura 2000.</terms:description>
        <terms:description xml:lang="en">The LIFE Integrated Project Marha (Marine Habitats) aims to restore and maintain the favourable conservation status of natural marine habitats in mainland France. From 2018 to 2025, more than 650 actions involving assessment, experimentation, management, awareness-raising and training were implemented, mobilising all stakeholders involved in the management of Natura 2000 marine sites.</terms:description>
        <terms:description xml:lang="el">Το ολοκληρωμένο πρόγραμμα LIFE Marha (Marine Habitats) στοχεύει στην αποκατάσταση και διατήρηση της καλής κατάστασης διατήρησης των φυσικών θαλάσσιων οικοτόπων στη μητροπολιτική Γαλλία. Από το 2018 έως το 2025, υλοποιήθηκαν περισσότερες από 650 δράσεις αξιολόγησης, πειραματισμού, διαχείρισης, ευαισθητοποίησης και κατάρτισης, κινητοποιώντας το σύνολο των φορέων που εμπλέκονται στη διαχείριση των θαλάσσιων περιοχών Natura 2000.</terms:description>
        <terms:title xml:lang="el">LIFE Marha</terms:title>
        <terms:title xml:lang="en">LIFE Marha</terms:title>
        <terms:title xml:lang="es">LIFE Marha</terms:title>
        <terms:title xml:lang="fr">LIFE Marha</terms:title>
        <terms:title xml:lang="it">LIFE Marha</terms:title>
        <terms:title xml:lang="no">LIFE Marha</terms:title>
        <terms:title xml:lang="pt">LIFE Marha</terms:title>
        <terms:title xml:lang="ro">LIFE Marha</terms:title>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="el">LIFE Marha</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">LIFE Marha</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="es">LIFE Marha</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="fr">LIFE Marha</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="it">LIFE Marha</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="no">LIFE Marha</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="pt">LIFE Marha</rdfs:label>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="ro">LIFE Marha</rdfs:label>
        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="el">LIFE Marha</skos:prefLabel>
        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">LIFE Marha</skos:prefLabel>
